    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were scoped out as not required at MRL 2. The discretization error factor achieved level 2 against a required level of 3; the team judged that the GCI exceedances at high-speed operating points are conservative in direction and do not affect the relative hemolysis ranking conclusion. On this basis the overall assessment is Accepted and the model is considered fit for the stated COU.",
